  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>(You must have Latent Forgemaster I)<br />Beginning at 11th level, by spending a charge from a Kit chosen by Latent Forgemaster I or II, and spending an hour inside of an unoccupied space, you can make a <strong>Temporary Sealsmith Forge</strong> that lasts for 24 hours. For the duration, you can craft Weapon or Armor Seals (depending on kit chosen) at full price.</p>",
